<favourite xmlns="http://www.hymnal.net/favourite" type="ts" num="9211" month="11" day="16" year="2012">
    <article author="Julia Yue" city="Auckland" provst="" country="New Zealand" month="11" day="16" year="2012">每次唱，都不能不流泪。主啊，我们何等地羡慕你！何等爱你！愿你快来！！！愿今日的爱满足你心！！！！</article>
    <article author="Lixia Yu" city="Ningbo" provst="Zhejiang" country="China" month="5" day="27" year="2012">感谢赞美你，这首歌很有感觉，主啊，求你让我做个单纯的人，我愿意一生做你疯狂爱人！</article>
    <article author="AMY" city="Ningbo" provst="Zhejiang" country="China" month="5" day="27" year="2012">主啊，求你赎回我所有的光阴，愿意单纯地向着你，让我一生做你疯狂爱人！</article>
    <article author="Egliang" city="Ningbo" provst="Zhejiang" country="China" month="2" day="10" year="2012">Lord Jesus! I love You! I need You!</article>
    <article author="Andrew Huang" city="Richmond" provst="BC" country="Canada" month="1" day="15" year="2012">心思置于肉体，就是死；心思置于灵，乃是生命平安。--罗八6</article>
    <article author="Rebecca Hu" city="Beijing" provst="" country="China" month="11" day="10" year="2011">这是我最喜欢的一首歌。一直想找到音乐文本反复听，终于找到了。感谢主！</article>
    <article author="Enosh Leong" city="Kota Kinabalu" provst="Sabah" country="Malaysia" month="10" day="8" year="2011">唱的時候一面奉獻禱告，把詩歌的負擔唱出來</article>
